snippet.title: Doomed in 59 Seconds: Real Stories from the Flight That Never Landed | Ahmedabad Plane Crash
snippet.description:
Doomed in 59 Seconds: Real Stories from the Flight That Never Landed | Ahmedabad Plane Crash
In just 59 seconds, everything changed. What began as a routine flight filled with excited families, first-time flyers, and last-minute goodbye texts, turned into an unthinkable tragedy. As AI 171 took off, some passengers were heading home, others off to summer vacations â€” none of them knowing it would be their final journey. This video reconstructs the flight moment by moment: from the unusual dip at 14 seconds, to the explosion at 30 seconds. No "landed safely" messages followed. Instead, chaos unfolded on the ground â€” hospitals overwhelmed, families waiting, lives shattered. Survivors speak: one missed the flight by just hours, another saved by traffic, one more who jumped. This is more than a crash; itâ€™s a story of loss, fate, and the fragile seconds that change everything.
Emergency number 18005691444

snippet.title: GRILLED CHICKEN WINGS | Juicy BBQ Chicken Wings Grilled in Village | Smoky Charcoal Chicken Recipe
snippet.description:
In this video, we prepare delicious grilled chicken wings using a traditional charcoal firewood grill in our village. The chicken wings are marinated with a homemade blend of spices, curd, and a hint of lemon for that perfect tang. Cooked slowly over glowing embers, every bite is juicy, smoky, and full of authentic BBQ flavor.

Watch as we roast the wings to golden perfection on skewers, turning them gently to prevent burning and retain moisture. The smoky aroma, the natural outdoor cooking, and the crispy edges come together to make this one of the best chicken recipes we'll ever try.

nl-NL.title: GEGRILDE KIPPENVLEUGELS | Sappige BBQ-kippenvleugels gegrild in Village | Recept voor gerookte ho...
nl-NL.description:
In deze video bereiden we heerlijke gegrilde kippenvleugels op een traditionele houtskoolgrill in ons dorp. De kippenvleugels worden gemarineerd met een zelfgemaakte mix van kruiden, wrongel en een vleugje citroen voor die perfecte pittigheid. Langzaam gegaard boven gloeiende kolen, is elke hap sappig, rokerig en vol authentieke BBQ-smaak.

Zie hoe we de vleugels goudbruin roosteren aan spiesjes, waarbij we ze voorzichtig omdraaien om aanbranden te voorkomen en de sappigheid te behouden. De rokerige geur, het natuurlijke buitengaren en de knapperige randjes zorgen er samen voor dat dit een van de beste kiprecepten is die we ooit zullen proberen.

id.title: SAYAP AYAM PANGGANG | Sayap Ayam Panggang Lezat di Desa | Resep Ayam Panggang Arang Asap
id.description:
Dalam video ini, kami menyiapkan sayap ayam panggang yang lezat menggunakan panggangan arang kayu bakar tradisional di desa kami. Sayap ayam direndam dengan campuran rempah-rempah, dadih, dan sedikit lemon buatan sendiri untuk rasa asam yang sempurna. Dimasak perlahan di atas bara api yang menyala, setiap gigitannya berair, berasap, dan penuh dengan cita rasa BBQ yang autentik.

Saksikan saat kami memanggang sayap hingga keemasan sempurna di tusuk sate, membaliknya dengan lembut agar tidak gosong dan mempertahankan kelembapan. Aroma berasap, masakan alami di luar ruangan, dan tepian yang renyah berpadu menjadikan ini salah satu resep ayam terbaik yang pernah kami coba.

snippet.title: Man Escapes Air India Crash by One Flight - He Noticed Something Strange!
snippet.description:
Man Escapes Air India Crash by One Flight - He Noticed Something Strange!


A devastating incident involving Air India Flight 171â€”a Boeing 787-8 Dreamlinerâ€”has resulted in numerous fatalities after the aircraft crashed shortly after takeoff from Ahmedabad airport on its way to London. A passenger who had traveled on the same aircraft just two hours earlier, on a Delhi-to-Ahmedabad leg, took to social media to report troubling technical issues. He pointed out that the air conditioning and in-flight entertainment systems were not functioning, sparking serious concerns about the planeâ€™s upkeep and overall safety.

The tragedy has put a renewed spotlight on Air Indiaâ€™s operational practices, with the passengerâ€™s account raising further doubts about the airline's service standards and safety track record. The Boeing 787-8, equipped with Rolls Royce Trent 1000 engines, has previously encountered mechanical challengesâ€”now prompting investigations into potential system failures or deliberate interference. Indian aviation authorities, in coordination with their British counterparts, are actively probing the cause of the crash amid growing global criticism.

This incident has once again ignited global conversations about the dependability of modern aircraft and the critical need for strict maintenance routines. It also revives scrutiny of Air Indiaâ€™s long-standing reputation, frequently ranked among the least reliable carriers worldwide.

en.description:
Man Escapes Air India Crash by One Flight - He Noticed Something Strange!


A devastating incident involving Air India Flight 171â€”a Boeing 787-8 Dreamlinerâ€”has resulted in numerous fatalities after the aircraft crashed shortly after takeoff from Ahmedabad airport on its way to London. A passenger who had traveled on the same aircraft just two hours earlier, on a Delhi-to-Ahmedabad leg, took to social media to report troubling technical issues. He pointed out that the air conditioning and in-flight entertainment systems were not functioning, sparking serious concerns about the planeâ€™s upkeep and overall safety.

The tragedy has put a renewed spotlight on Air Indiaâ€™s operational practices, with the passengerâ€™s account raising further doubts about the airline's service standards and safety track record. The Boeing 787-8, equipped with Rolls Royce Trent 1000 engines, has previously encountered mechanical challengesâ€”now prompting investigations into potential system failures or deliberate interference. Indian aviation authorities, in coordination with their British counterparts, are actively probing the cause of the crash amid growing global criticism.

This incident has once again ignited global conversations about the dependability of modern aircraft and the critical need for strict maintenance routines. It also revives scrutiny of Air Indiaâ€™s long-standing reputation, frequently ranked among the least reliable carriers worldwide.

snippet.title: Young Air India Crew Member From Manipur Killed in Flight AI171 Crash
snippet.description:
Just hours before boarding Air India Flight AI171 to London, 21-year-old Nganthoi Sharma from Manipur made a final call to her sister. Minutes after takeoff, the aircraft crashed near Ahmedabad, leaving her family in shock and mourning. As DNA identification continues, her loved ones remember a vibrant young woman who followed her dreams into the skiesâ€”only to be lost too soon.

*Crossing India for Free ~ Original by Monkey Magic*
about Day 13 
In this video I hitchhike from New Delhi to Ratlam in a truck, the idea was to go and stand on the Delhi - Mumbai Expressway and go wherever the truck takes me. I wanted to enter the world of truck drivers, how they do what they do. How do they manage to drive for hours and hours, where do they eat? How do they wash? Where do they sleep? How much do they earn? 

This video answers every question from a very humane perspective. 

 *About Crossing India for FREE (K2K)* ğŸ‡®ğŸ‡³
What was the last time you pushed yourself out of your comfort zone? 

This is a super fun reality show series where I have to reach Kanyakumari for Free and if I spend some money on the road then I have to earn that money back by doing random jobs on the road itself.

snippet.title: Air India flight crash: What We Know So Far
snippet.description:
#planecrash #Ahmedabadcrash #airindiaplanecrash

Former chief minister of Gujarat, Vijay Rupani's name was in the list of passengers onboard the Air India flight that crashed near the Ahmedabad International Airport on Thursday. However, sources close to him told TNIE he was not on board and had taken a different flight.

snippet.title: Squid Game: Season 3 | Final Games Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Itâ€™s time to play the final games. Squid Game 3 premieres June 27, only on Netflix.

From Season 1 to Season 3, Gi-hunâ€™s been fighting until the very end. Will he beat the deadly Squid Game? Or will the Front Man continue to be one step ahead?

More info on Squid Game Season 3:
A failed rebellion, the death of a friend, and a secret betrayal. Picking up in the aftermath of Season 2â€™s bloody cliffhanger, the third and final season of Netflixâ€™s most popular series finds Gi-hun, a.k.a. Player 456, at his lowest point yet. But the Squid Game stops for no one, so Gi-hun will be forced to make some important choices in the face of overwhelming despair as he and the surviving players are thrust into deadlier games that test everyoneâ€™s resolve. With each round, their choices lead to increasingly grave consequences. Meanwhile, In-ho resumes his role as Front Man to welcome the mysterious VIPs, and his brother Jun-ho continues his search for the elusive island, unaware thereâ€™s a traitor in their midst. Will Gi-hun make the right decisions, or will Front Man finally break his spirit?
Director Hwang Dong-hyuk, who made history at the 74th Primetime EmmysÂ®, becoming the first Asian to win Outstanding Directing for a Drama Series, once again helms the series as director, writer, and producer. Season 3 stars Lee Jung-jae, Lee Byung-hun, Yim Si-wan, Kang Ha-neul, Wi Ha-jun, Park Gyu-young, Park Sung-hoon, Yang Dong-geun, Kang Ae-sim, Jo Yu-ri, Chae Kuk-hee, Lee David, Roh Jae-won, and Jun Suk-ho, with special appearance by Park Hee-soon.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81615967

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Squid Game: Season 3 | Final Games Trailer | Netflix

New games. Old foes. Player 456 and the Front Man clash in a final showdown of moral dilemmas and pulse-racing challenges. Who will emerge victorious?

Ghatak :-
Kashi Nath is a kind-hearted wrestler and the dutiful adopted son of Shambhu Nath, living in Banaras. Shambhu Nath, who was a freedom fighter awarded with the Tambra Patra, is an honourable and respectable man in town. Kashi, along with Shambhu, comes to Mumbai for medical treatment for Shambhu and stays with his brother, Shiv Nath. Kashi meets Gauri in the colony and starts liking her. He learns that the colony is being terrorized by the tyrannical gangster, Katya, along with his six brothers. Before Kashi's arrival, a resident named Sachdev tried to initiate a revolt against Katya, but got ruthlessly killed by him, thereby making Malti, Sachdev's wife, go mad. Katya and his brothers become enemies with Kashi when he beats up their goons in the process of roughing up Malti.

snippet.title: ENG vs WI | 3rd T20I | Cricket Highlights | West Indies Tour Of England | 10th June 2025
snippet.description:
England secured a dominant 37-run victory over West Indies in the 3rd T20I at Utilita Bowl, Southampton. Batting first, England posted a massive 248/3 in 20 overs, with Ben Duckett leading the charge with an explosive 84 off 46 balls. West Indies fought hard but fell short, managing 211/8 in their chase. With this win, England completed a 3-0 series sweep, asserting their dominance in the shortest format.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Episode 4403: Trip Ki Taiyyari

Jethalal gears up for his upcoming trip to the Himalayas, and the colony members also express interest. At the same time, he carefully explains to Bapuji how to handle the shop while he's away. Will Bapuji manage smoothly?

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - promotes 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), a Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Ed Sheeran - Sapphire (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Listen to 'Sapphire' now: https://es.lnk.to/sapphireID

"Sapphire was the first song I finished for Play that made me know where the album was heading. It's why I finished the recording process in Goa surrounded by some of the best musicians in India. It was an incredible creative process. I shot the music video with Liam Pethick and Nic Minns across my India tour earlier this year, we wanted to showcase the beauty and breadth of the country and its culture. The final jigsaw piece for me was getting @Official_ArijitSingh on the record, but it was a journey to get there and such an amazing day of music and family. Me and him have done a full Punjabi version of the song that will come out in the next few weeks, which has a lot more of him on it. This is the album version of the song, and my favourite song on the album. Hope you guys love it. Sapphire out now" - Ed x

Pre-order 'Play' out September 12: https://es.lnk.to/playID

localized.title: Ed Sheeran - Sapphire (Official Music Video)
localized.description:
Listen to 'Sapphire' now: https://es.lnk.to/sapphireID

"Sapphire was the first song I finished for Play that made me know where the album was heading. It's why I finished the recording process in Goa surrounded by some of the best musicians in India. It was an incredible creative process. I shot the music video with Liam Pethick and Nic Minns across my India tour earlier this year, we wanted to showcase the beauty and breadth of the country and its culture. The final jigsaw piece for me was getting @Official_ArijitSingh on the record, but it was a journey to get there and such an amazing day of music and family. Me and him have done a full Punjabi version of the song that will come out in the next few weeks, which has a lot more of him on it. This is the album version of the song, and my favourite song on the album. Hope you guys love it. Sapphire out now" - Ed x
